### -----------------------------
### CART API TESTS
### -----------------------------

### 1. Check product before adding (happy path)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/items/check?walletAddress=0x9c8D6Fd696Ba2172e9Da56B2a48A6Fe218423774&productId=76&quantity=2

### 1a. Check product with invalid quantity (error)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/items/check?walletAddress=0x9c8D6Fd696Ba2172e9Da56B2a48A6Fe218423774&productId=1&quantity=0

### 1b. Check product not found (error)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/items/check?walletAddress=0x9c8D6Fd696Ba2172e9Da56B2a48A6Fe218423774&productId=1&quantity=1

---

### 2. Create new cart item (happy path)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletAddress": "0x9c8D6Fd696Ba2172e9Da56B2a48A6Fe218423774",
  "productId": 76,
  "quantity": 1,
  "checkoutAction": "BuyAndTransfer"
}

### 2a. Create with invalid checkoutAction (error)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletAddress": "0x9c8D6Fd696Ba2172e9Da56B2a48A6Fe218423774",
  "productId": 76,
  "quantity": 1,
  "checkoutAction": "INVALID_ACTION"
}

---

### 3. Get active cart items (happy path)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/items?walletAddress=0x9c8D6Fd696Ba2172e9Da56B2a48A6Fe218423774

### 3a. Get without walletAddress (error)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cart/items

---

### 4. Update existing cart item (happy path)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/cart/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "walletAddress": "0x9c8D6Fd696Ba2172e9Da56B2a48A6Fe218423774",
  "quantity": 5
}

---

### 5. Delete (soft remove) cart item
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/cart/items/1

